{"defs":{},"properties":[{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/hasValuesFrom","description":"A cdi:DescriptorValueDomain enumerating the codes that can appear in the descriptor column, each paired (via cdif:isDefinedBy) with the RepresentedVariable that the code names.","required":true,"sources":["bblocks://cdif.bbr.metadata.cdifProperties.cdifDescriptorVariable"],"effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/hasValuesFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/takesValuesFrom","description":"Ordered list of descriptor entries. Each entry has a cdif:value (the code as it appears in the descriptor column) and a cdif:isDefinedBy pointer to the RepresentedVariable that the code names.","required":true,"schema_type":"array","sources":["bblocks://cdif.bbr.metadata.cdifProperties.cdifDescriptorVariable"],"effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/takesValuesFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:value"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/value","description":"The code value as it appears in the descriptor column.","required":true,"schema_type":"string","sources":["bblocks://cdif.bbr.metadata.cdifProperties.cdifDescriptorVariable"],"effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/value"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/isDefinedBy","required":true,"sources":["bblocks://cdif.bbr.metadata.cdifProperties.cdifDescriptorVariable"],"effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/isDefinedBy"},{"path":["cdi:name"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name","description":"Human understandable name (linguistic signifier, word, phrase, or mnemonic). May follow ISO/IEC 11179-5 naming principles, and have context provided to specify usage.","schema_type":"array","sources":["bblocks://cdif.bbr.metadata.cdifProperties.cdifDescriptorVariable"],"effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdif:uses_Concept"],"schema_type":"array"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:name"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name","description":"Human understandable name (linguistic signifier, word, phrase, or mnemonic). May follow ISO/IEC 11179-5 naming principles, and have context provided to specify usage.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:identifier"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier","description":"Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:externalDefinition"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/externalDefinition","description":"A reference to an external definition of a concept (that is, a concept which is described outside the content of the DDI-CDI metadata description). An example is a SKOS concept. The definition property is assumed to duplicate the external one referenced if externalDefinition is used. Other corresponding properties are assumed to be included unchanged if used.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/externalDefinition"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:displayLabel"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel","description":"A human-readable display label for the object. Supports the use of multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:definition"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/definition","description":"Natural language statement conveying the meaning of a concept, differentiating it from other concepts. Supports the use of multiple languages and structured text. 'externalDefinition' can't be used if 'definition' is used.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/definition"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:unitOfMeasureKind"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/unitOfMeasureKind","description":"Kind of unit of measure, so that it may be prone to translation to equivalent UOMs. Example values include \"acceleration,\" \"temperature,\" \"salinity\", etc. This description exists at the conceptual level, indicating a limitation on the type of representations which may be used for the variable as it is made more concrete.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/unitOfMeasureKind"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/measures","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/measures"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures","cdi:descriptiveText"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/descriptiveText","description":"A short natural language account of the characteristics of the object.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/descriptiveText"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures","cdi:definition"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/definition","description":"Natural language statement conveying the meaning of a concept, differentiating it from other concepts. Supports the use of multiple languages and structured text. 'externalDefinition' can't be used if 'definition' is used.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/definition"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures","cdi:displayLabel"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel","description":"A human-readable display label for the object. Supports the use of multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures","cdi:externalDefinition"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/externalDefinition","description":"A reference to an external definition of a concept (that is, a concept which is described outside the content of the DDI-CDI metadata description). An example is a SKOS concept. The definition property is assumed to duplicate the external one referenced if externalDefinition is used. Other corresponding properties are assumed to be included unchanged if used.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/externalDefinition"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures","cdi:identifier"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier","description":"Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures","cdi:name"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name","description":"Human understandable name (linguistic signifier, word, phrase, or mnemonic). May follow ISO/IEC 11179-5 naming principles, and have context provided to specify usage.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:measures","cdif:uses_Concept"],"schema_type":"array"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveConceptsFrom"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSubstantiveConceptsFrom","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSubstantiveConceptsFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveConceptsFrom","cdi:displayLabel"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel","description":"A human-readable display label for the object. Supports the use of multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveConceptsFrom","cdi:identifier"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier","description":"Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/isDescribedBy","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/isDescribedBy"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesConceptsFrom","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesConceptsFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSentinelConceptsFrom","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSentinelConceptsFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:displayLabel"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel","description":"A human-readable display label for the object. Supports the use of multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/displayLabel"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:identifier"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier","description":"Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/isDescribedBy","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/isDescribedBy"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:regularExpression"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/regularExpression","description":"A regular expression where strings matching the expression belong to the set of valid values. Use typeOfContent to specify the syntax of the regularExpression found in content.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/regularExpression"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:regularExpression","cdi:typeOfContent"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/typeOfContent","description":"Optional use of a controlled vocabulary to specifically type the associated content.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/typeOfContent"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:regularExpression","cdif:content"],"description":"Content of the property expressed as a simple string.","schema_type":"string"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:minimumValueInclusive"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/minimumValueInclusive","description":"A string denoting the minimum possible value. From the W3C Recommendation \"Metadata Vocabulary for Tabular Data\" (https://www.w3.org/TR/tabular-metadata/) 5.11.2: \"minimum: An atomic property that contains a single number or string that is the minimum valid value (inclusive); equivalent to minInclusive. The value of this property becomes the minimum annotation for the described datatype. See Value Constraints in [tabular-data-model] for details.\"","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/minimumValueInclusive"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:minimumValueExclusive"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/minimumValueExclusive","description":"A string denoting the minimum possible value (excluding this value). From the W3C Recommendation \"Metadata Vocabulary for Tabular Data\" (https://www.w3.org/TR/tabular-metadata/) 5.11.2: \"minExclusive: An atomic property that contains a single number or string that is the minimum valid value (exclusive). The value of this property becomes the minimum exclusive annotation for the described datatype. See Value Constraints in [tabular-data-model] for details.\"","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/minimumValueExclusive"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:maximumValueInclusive"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/maximumValueInclusive","description":"A string denoting the maximum possible value. From the W3C Recommendation \"Metadata Vocabulary for Tabular Data\" (https://www.w3.org/TR/tabular-metadata/) 5.11.2: \"maximum: An atomic property that contains a single number or string that is the maximum valid value (inclusive); equivalent to maxInclusive. The value of this property becomes the maximum annotation for the described datatype. See Value Constraints in [tabular-data-model] for details.\"","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/maximumValueInclusive"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:maximumValueExclusive"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/maximumValueExclusive","description":"A string denoting the maximum possible value (excluding this value). From the W3C Recommendation \"Metadata Vocabulary for Tabular Data\" (https://www.w3.org/TR/tabular-metadata/) 5.11.2: \"maxExclusive: An atomic property that contains a single number or string that is the maximum valid value (exclusive). The value of this property becomes the maximum exclusive annotation for the described datatype. See Value Constraints in [tabular-data-model] for details.\"","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/maximumValueExclusive"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:logicalExpression"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/logicalExpression","description":"A logical expression where the values of \"x\" making the expression true are the members of the set of valid values. For example, \"(all reals x such that x > 0)\" describes the real numbers greater than 0.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/logicalExpression"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:identifier"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier","description":"Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:formatPattern"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/formatPattern","description":"A pattern for a number as described in Unicode Locale Data Markup Language (LDML) (http://www.unicode.org/reports/tr35/tr35.html) Part 3: Numbers (http://www.unicode.org/reports/tr35/tr35-numbers.html#Number_Format_Patterns) and Part 4. Dates (http://www.unicode.org/reports/tr35/tr35-dates.html#Date_Format_Patterns) . Examples would be #,##0.### to describe the pattern for a decimal number, or yyyy.MM.dd G 'at' HH:mm:ss zzz for a datetime pattern.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/formatPattern"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:description"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/description","description":"A formal description of the set of values in human-readable language.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/description"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:isDescribedBy","cdi:classificationLevel"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/classificationLevel","description":"Indicates the type of relationship, nominal, ordinal, interval, ratio, or continuous. Use where appropriate for the representation type.","schema_type":"string","enum":["Continuous","Interval","Nominal","Ordinal","Ratio"],"effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/classificationLevel"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesConceptsFrom","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesConceptsFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:purpose"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/purpose","description":"Intent or reason for the object/the description of the object.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/purpose"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdif:has_Concept"],"schema_type":"array"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy_Concept"],"schema_type":"array"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:name"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name","description":"Human understandable name (liguistic signifier, word, phrase, or mnemonic). May follow ISO/IEC 11179-5 naming principles, and have context provided to specify usage.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/name"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:identifier"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier","description":"Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:externalDefinition"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/externalDefinition","description":"A reference to an external definition of a concept (that is, a concept which is described outside the content of the DDI-CDI metadata description). An example is a SKOS concept. The definition property is assumed to duplicate the external one referenced if externalDefinition is used. Other corresponding properties are assumed to be included unchanged if used.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/externalDefinition"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:externalDefinition","schema:description"],"description":"Human-readable description of the reference.","schema_type":"string"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:externalDefinition","schema:name"],"description":"Human-readable name of the referenced resource.","schema_type":"string"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:externalDefinition","schema:url"],"description":"URL of the referenced resource.","schema_type":"string","format":"uri"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelConceptsFrom","cdi:takesConceptsFrom","cdi:allowsDuplicates"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/allowsDuplicates","description":"If value is False, the members are unique within the collection - if True, there may be duplicates. (Note that a mathematical \u201cbag\u201d permits duplicates and is unordered - a \u201cset\u201d does not have duplicates and may be ordered.)","schema_type":"boolean","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/allowsDuplicates"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:descriptiveText"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/descriptiveText","description":"A short natural language account of the characteristics of the object.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/descriptiveText"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:simpleUnitOfMeasure"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/simpleUnitOfMeasure","description":"The unit in which the data values are measured (kg, pound, euro), expressed as a simple string, in cases where no additional information is available (in the legacy system) or needed (as in the case of broad agreement within the community of use [i.e., ISO country codes, currencies, etc. in SDMX])","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/simpleUnitOfMeasure"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveValuesFrom"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSubstantiveValuesFrom","description":"The substantive value domain for this RepresentedVariable - the set of valid, meaningful values (RepresentedVariable.takesSubstantiveValuesFrom).","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSubstantiveValuesFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/takesValuesFrom","effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/takesValuesFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveValuesFrom","cdif:displayLabel"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/displayLabel","description":"A human-readable display label for the object. Supports the use of multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/displayLabel"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSubstantiveValuesFrom","cdif:recommendedDataType"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/recommendedDataType","description":"The data types that are recommended for use with this domain.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/recommendedDataType"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelValuesFrom"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSentinelValuesFrom","description":"Sentinel (missing / not-applicable) value domain(s) for this RepresentedVariable (RepresentedVariable.takesSentinelValuesFrom).","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/takesSentinelValuesFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/takesValuesFrom","effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/takesValuesFrom"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:purpose"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/purpose","description":"Intent or reason for the object/the description of the obj