ier string. E.g. 10.5066/F7VX0DMQ","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://schema.org/value"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:identifier","schema:propertyID"],"id":"http://schema.org/propertyID","description":"In this context for the schema:PropertyValue, this field is an identifier for the identifier schema, e.g. DOI, ARK.  Get values from https://registry.identifiers.org/registry/ for interoperability","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://schema.org/propertyID"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelValuesFrom","cdif:displayLabel"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/displayLabel","description":"A human-readable display label for the object. Supports the use of multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/displayLabel"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:takesSentinelValuesFrom","cdif:recommendedDataType"],"id":"https://cdif.org/0.1/recommendedDataType","description":"The data types that are recommended for use with this domain.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/recommendedDataType"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:hasIntendedDataType"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/hasIntendedDataType","description":"The data type intended to be used by this variable. Supports the optional use of an external controlled vocabulary.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/hasIntendedDataType"},{"path":["cdif:hasValuesFrom","cdif:takesValuesFrom","cdif:isDefinedBy","cdi:describedUnitOfMeasure"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/describedUnitOfMeasure","description":"The unit in which the data values are measur